  <section>
    <h1>We are a worker cooperative</h1>
    <p>
      Worker cooperatives, as defined by
      <%= link_to "The Tech Co-op Network", "http://techworker.coop/", target: "_blank" %>,
      are "businesses owned and democratically controlled by" their workers.
      As a democratically controlled business, we network with other like-minded
      groups. We are members of:
    </p>

    <div class="membership">
      <div class="blurb">
        <%= image_tag "usfwc.png" %>
        <div>
          <h4><%= link_to "The United States Federation of Worker Coops", "http://usworker.coop/", target: "_blank" %></h4>
          <p>A network of democratically-owned businesses in the United States</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blurb">
        <%= image_tag "tech-coop-network.png" %>
        <div>
          <h4><%= link_to "The Tech Co-op Network", "http://techworker.coop/", target: "_blank" %></h4>
          <p>A network of North American worker cooperatives focused on technology</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- <p>As our logo reflects, we are based in Michigan helping to bring life back into our home.</p> -->
